snippet.title: NAMEKO - Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
The adventure of Ko, in his quest to save all the planets. A Beat ‘em Up game developed by GreenKiwi Studios and powered by IPLeiria.

Game developer: Marcelo Pereira
Sound designer: Hugo Goncalves
Game Designer: Pedro Paixão
3D artist: Hugo Roldao
